        <p>
          Rather than viewing the <strong>entourage effect</strong> as just THC + terpenes + CBD, Meiri urges us to reconceive it as a <strong>principle of polypharmacy</strong>&mdash;where <strong>multiple active compounds simultaneously target multiple mechanisms</strong> within a complex biological condition.
